25|$|The Government's {{low carbon}} {{buildings}} programme {{was launched in}} 2006 to replace the earlier Clear Skies and Solar PV programmes. It offers grants towards the costs of solar thermal heating, small wind turbine, micro hydro, <b>ground</b> <b>source</b> <b>heat</b> <b>pump,</b> and biomass installations. As of January 2007 funding for grants is proving insufficient to meet demand.|$|E
